All Implemented Interfaces:
DataWidget, MapView, MultiDataWidget, Widget, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.InternalEObject
public class MapViewImpl
extends DataWidgetImpl
implements MapView

An implementation of the model object 'Map View'.

The following features are implemented:

  • Multi Data Binding
  • Map Id
  • Start Envelope Spec
  • Max Envelope Spec
  • Scale Envelope Spec
  • Num Levels
  • Edit Data Binding
  • Gadgets
  • No Click When Disabled
  • No Edit When Disabled
  • No Zoom When Disabled
  • No Pan When Disabled
